decisionBody: Toronto and East York Community Council
noticeDescription: Take notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law No. 1386-2017 to designate 2430 and 2434 Yonge Street (including the entrance address at 2436 Yonge Street) (Eglinton-Lawrence – Ward 16) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
